sequenceDiagram
    participant browser
    participant server

    Type a note and click "Save"

    browser->>browser: JS event handler intercepts form submit
    browser->>browser: Prevent default page reload
    browser->>browser: Create note object with content + date

    browser->>server: POST https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/new_note
    activate server
    Note right of server: Server stores the new note in memory/database
    server-->>browser: 201 Created (or redirect response)
    deactivate server

    Note right of browser: Browser updates UI (or reloads notes list)

    browser->>server: GET https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/data.json
    activate server
    server-->>browser: Updated notes JSON
    deactivate server

    browser->>browser: JS renders updated notes to the page
